data.description: Country living at its best in this home on 3.45 Acres MOL in Sweetwater Oklahoma  For Sale. Beautiful farm home situated on almost 4 acres with a well and storm shelter. Newer windows, metal roof and exterior paint welcome you to this quaint home. Adorable corner sink in the guest bath and a walk-in shower in the primary bath that is handicapped-accessible as well as the front of the home that has a concrete ramp.  Outbuilds/shops also on the property. Enjoy the rural setting that has all the solitude one could want or need. Make your private showing appointment today.  USDA, FHA, VA Eligible!
